quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  44,19,"“Le se ikhohomose khahlanong le Allah: Hobane ke tla ho lona ka matla a Hae"
  44,20,"“Ke kopile ts’ireletso ho Mong’a ka, e leng Mong’a lona, khahlanong le tlhaselo ho tsoa ho lona"
  44,21,"“Haeba le sa nkholoe, le tsamaele thoko le ‘na.”"
  44,22,"(Empa ba ne ba le makoebeta) Eaba o bitsa ho Mong’a hae: “Bana ruri ke batho ba qoetseng sebeng”"
  44,23,"(Karabo ea eba): “Tsamaea le makhabunyane a Ka bosiu: hobane ruri le tla saloa morao"
  44,24,"“Le siee leoatle le bulehile ka lehare: hobane ke lebotho le loketseng ho khang’oa ke metsi.”"
  44,25,Ke lirapa le liliba tse kae tseo ba li siileng morao
  44,26,"Le masimo, le meaho e majaba-jaba"
  44,27,Le maruo ao ban eng ba ikhants’a ka ona
  44,28,E joalo (qetello ea bona) Re entse hore batho ba bang e be majalefa(a lintho tsa bona)
  44,29,Leholimo le lefats’e ha li ea ka tsa keleketlisa keleli sebakeng sa bona; kapa nako ea bona ea eketsoa
  44,30,Re ile Ra lopolla Bana ba Israele Kotlong e soabisang
  44,31,Ho tsoa ho Faro. Hobane ene e le e mong oa baikhohomosi har’a batloli ba meeli ba feteletseng
  44,32,Re ba khethile ka morero holim’a lichaba tsohle
  44,33,"Ra ba neha Lits’upiso, tse neng li jere teko e hlakileng"
  44,34,Haele bona ba re Kannete
  44,35,"“Ha ho letho ka nqane ho lefu, ha re na ho tsosoa hape"
  44,36,"“Khutlisa bo-ntat’a moholo’a rona, haeba seo u se buang ke ‘nete!”"
  44,37,"Eng! Ba feta batho ba Tubba, le ba bileng teng pele ho bona? Re ile Ra ba timetsa, hobane e ne e le batho ba loebaloebang sebeng"
  44,38,"Ha Re’a hlola maholimo le lefats’e le tsohle tse teng lipakeng tsa tsona, ka bosaoana"
  44,39,Ha Re’a lihlolla letho haese ka toka; empa bongata ba bona ha bo utloisise